{
  "overview": "The Medishetty (SOMO) Laboratory at IIT Bhilai is a synthesis-and-characterization facility purpose-built for solid-state photochemistry, crystal engineering, and inorganic materials research. The lab combines in-house instrumentation with shared institutional access to advanced spectroscopy, diffraction, and electron microscopy facilities.",
