    "Single-crystal growth and recrystallisation",
    "Photochemical reaction monitoring under controlled wavelengths",
    "Solid-state structural characterization",
    "Photo-physical and luminescence measurements",
    "Electrochemical cycling of battery materials",
    "Thermal analysis and polymorph studies"
  ],
